# Drift Master

A browser-based drift racing game built with HTML5 Canvas and JavaScript.

## Features
- Realistic drift physics
- Speedometer, drift angle, lap timer
- Car selection with unique stats
- Mobile-friendly UI
- Expandable for multiplayer and leaderboards

## How to Play
- Arrow keys to drive
- Select your car from the dropdown
- Drift inside the track and beat your lap time

## Setup
Just open `index.html` in your browser or host it via GitHub Pages.

